title: How to Make Cake Batter Cookies
description: What’s a football tailgate party without confetti? Fortunately, this confetti is a lot tastier and easier to clean up! The easy Color Right™ QuickCount™ formulas make creating your favorite team colors a breeze. Make these for your tailgate party, homecoming game or youth football team—get everything you need for this easy cake batter cookie recipe right here.
